            <p>Welcome to <span class="green-text">Swole Goal</span>. A powerful tool to help you achieve all of your health and fitness goals. Fill out every field to recieve a customly tailored workout plan, as well as a personalized diet outline full of healthy food that maintains great taste.</p>
