    <section class="module parallax fitness" id="fitness">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Fitness</h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="module content">
        <hr style="width:50%" />
        <div class="container">
            <p>
                Our recommended guide will help you target every muscle group in a way that will help you reach your fitness goals. Our gym based plan takes 
                place in the heart of the gym with a core focus on weight training along side suplementary cardio exercises all based on your needs.
            </p>
            <p>
                We focus on a 4-5 day split which each workout day focusing on a specific muscle group. We'll give you all the exercises you need to kick start
                your gym regimen. Depending on the phisque you want to achieve we'll recommend certain cardiovascular activities as well!
            </p>
        </div>
        <hr style="width:50%" />
    </section>

    <section class="module parallax nutrition" id="nutrition">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Nutrition</h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="module content">
        <div class="container">
            <hr style="width:50%" />
            <p>IIFYM | Flexible Dieting</p>
            <p>
                Not so much of a diet as it is a way of living. Flexible dieting or IIFYM (If It Fits Your Macros) is just that, a non-restrictive
                way of eating that allows you to lose (or gain) weight by still eating all your favorite foods and meals.
            </p>
            <hr style="width:50%" />
        </div>
    </section>

